{"ID":"20260305082130-4fzlo5t","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-4fzlo5t","tags":"课程/CPP程序设计","title":"多态","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-uw5l0v7","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-uw5l0v7"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntags:\n  - 课程/CPP程序设计\ntitle: 多态\ndate created: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 10:51:12 上午\ndate modified: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 11:16:49 晚上\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-a0q5a0d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-a0q5a0d","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 什么是多态？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-alphks9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-alphks9","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“多态“一词来源于希腊语，意为“多种形态”。在面向对象编程中，多态指的是："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"允许一个接口有多种实现，或者说，允许一个对象在不同的上下文中表现出不同的行为。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单来说，多态的核心思想是："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“同一个操作作用于不同的对象，可以有不同的解释和行为。”"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-6pmcvo9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6pmcvo9","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"例如，我们说“动物发出声音”："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-mv963i2","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-mv963i2","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-b4ffn10","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-b4ffn10","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-tubgeid","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-tubgeid","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"狗发出声音，是“汪汪”叫。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zny5v48","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zny5v48","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-qbxyx86","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qbxyx86","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"猫发出声音，是“喵喵”叫。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-687aqik","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-687aqik","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-ccn1au2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ccn1au2","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鸟发出声音，是“叽叽喳喳”叫。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里的“发出声音”就是“同一个操作”，而狗、猫、鸟是“不同的对象”，它们各自有“不同的解释和行为”。这就是多态的直观体现。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-d5b3o7x","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-d5b3o7x","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 多态的目的"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-yxpexmi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-yxpexmi","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多态是面向对象编程中一个极其强大的特性，它带来了以下几个关键优势："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-k7lw7to","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-k7lw7to","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1 提高代码的灵活性和可扩展性："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-csld1bl","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-csld1bl","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-gfyi9tl","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gfyi9tl","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-6790zbj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6790zbj","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"无需修改现有代码："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 当你需要添加新的派生类时，你不需要修改使用基类指针/引用的现有代码。只需创建新的派生类并实现其特有的行为即可。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-evkxyga","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-evkxyga","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-kquo0iw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-kquo0iw","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 如果你有一个处理 ⁠Animal 对象的函数，当引入 ⁠Bird 类时，你不需要修改这个函数，它仍然可以通过 ⁠Animal* 正确地调用 ⁠Bird::makeSound()。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1qcjepq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1qcjepq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-l7ggrk8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l7ggrk8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"开放 - 封闭原则 (Open-Closed Principle)："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 多态是实现“开放 - 封闭原则”的关键。即软件实体（类、模块、函数等）应该对扩展开放，对修改封闭。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-wbbld7x","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-wbbld7x","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.2 简化代码结构，提高可维护性："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-q967nl6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-q967nl6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-8hu945a","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8hu945a","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-fzfuaa5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fzfuaa5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"统一接口："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 允许你使用一个统一的接口（基类指针/引用）来处理不同类型的对象。你无需为每种派生类型编写单独的代码分支（例如大量的 ⁠if-else if 或 ⁠switch 语句来判断对象类型）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-93hk1iv","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-93hk1iv","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-cy5pn2b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-cy5pn2b","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 一个 ⁠std::vector\u003cAnimal*\u003e 可以存储各种动物，然后通过循环统一调用 ⁠makeSound()，而不需要知道每个元素具体是 ⁠Dog 还是 ⁠Cat。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-55ml3e1","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-55ml3e1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-oatou96","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-oatou96","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"减少重复代码："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 避免了为相似功能在不同类中编写重复的代码。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-fjxgrwa","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fjxgrwa","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.3 实现抽象："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sets81e","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sets81e","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-48mr2oo","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-48mr2oo","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-l046jao","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l046jao","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多态允许你将注意力集中在“做什么”而不是“如何做”。基类定义了抽象的行为（接口），而派生类提供了具体的实现。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-v53xbnm","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-v53xbnm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-o2trnni","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-o2trnni","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ⁠Animal 类定义了 ⁠makeSound() 这个抽象行为，而具体的“如何叫”则由 ⁠Dog 和 ⁠Cat 等派生类去实现。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-mbdboji","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-mbdboji","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.4 框架和库设计的基础 ："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sx3f05c","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sx3f05c","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-gq7b075","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gq7b075","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-8v67ygg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8v67ygg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多态是设计可重用、可扩展的软件框架和库的基础。框架可以定义通用的行为和接口（通过虚函数），而用户可以通过继承和重写这些虚函数来定制自己的行为，而无需修改框架的核心代码。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-nwtxm4p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-nwtxm4p","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-72vqm43","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-72vqm43","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"aaa\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]}]}